About Us
/$
$
$
Shriners Believe in Brotherhood...  Shriners are a brotherhood of men committed to family, engaged in ongoing personal growth, and dedicated to providing care for children and families in need. Our backgrounds and interests are diverse, but we are bound together by our shared values and a desire to have fun, do good and build relationships that can last a lifetime.  To be a Shriner you have to be a Master Mason First.  Learn more about our organization below:

See our Rental Spaces
WEDDINGS
WELCOME TO THE SAHIB SHRINE CENTER OF SARASOTA, FL
Our 12,660 sq ft facility offers plenty of flexible event spaces perfect for your next special occasion.  The facility is comprised of a grand ballroom with room for more than 400 guests and a main hall that can be used for parties, weddings, anniversaries, meetings, conventions, conferences, social gatherings, exhibitions, banquets, specialty parties as well as class reunions or private groups.
Banquet services include a full-service bar, a full kitchen, a buffet, cocktail services, and fine-dining meal options.  You name it we got you covered.  Total Meetings Rooms are 4 and Largest Meeting room is 9000 sq ft.
​
Sahib also has a restaurant open to the public and a special outside Tiki Bar & Grill.  Come out and join in on the fun in the sun.
​
Contact us today, our staff is eager to help make your next event incredible!
Email
events@sahibshrine.org
or call us at
(941) 366-4449
. We would love to hear about your event.
